Package: hatpal
Type: Package
Title: APA clusters calling and analysis
Version: 0.9.1
Author: Heng Heng
Maintainer: Heng Heng <hengheng@genomics.cn>
Description: hatpal is a R package for APA identification & analysis in 3' end scrna-seq(10x etc.) 
    By clustering the polyA sites, we can get the high-confidence APA clusters and
    output a matrix for downstream analysis.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    kpeaks,
    GenomicAlignments,
    data.table,
    Ckmeans.1d.dp,
    Matrix,
    rtracklayer,
    IRanges
